  <para style="mt1">MARŨA MA JAKUBU</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Marũa maya maandĩkĩirwo Akristiano arĩa maahurunjũkĩte kũrĩa guothe gwathanagwo nĩ thirikari ya Roma. Marũa maya makuhĩ maandĩkĩtwo marĩ ma gũtaara andũ igũrũ rĩa mũtũũrĩre wa o mũthenya.</para>
  <para style="ip">Marũa maya maiyũrĩte mĩhaano ya kuonania wĩtĩkio ũkĩruta wĩra. Mataaro marĩa Jakubu aheanaga nĩ ta:</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓ndũkoorwo nĩ hinya ũngĩkorwo ũrĩ na thĩĩna,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓ndũgakue ngoro rĩrĩa wĩtĩkio waku ũkũgerio,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓ndũgatuĩke wa kũrakaraga na ihenya,</para>
  <para style="ili1">⁓ndũkendage arĩa marĩ na ũtonga gũkĩra arĩa athĩĩni.</para>
  <para style="im">Jakubu nĩoigĩte atĩ wĩtĩkio wa ma nĩwonanagia mũtũũrĩre mwega o ta ũrĩa mũtĩ mwega ũciaraga maciaro mega no ndũciaraga mĩigua.</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Jakubu, mũrũ wa nyina na Jesũ.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Mũtũũrĩre wa ma wa wĩtĩkio <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 1:1-27">1:1-27</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Maciaro ma wĩtĩkio mĩtũũrĩre-inĩ ya andũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 2:1-13">2:1-13</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Wĩtĩkio na ciĩko <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 2:14-26">2:14-26</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ũrutani wa kũmenyerera rũrĩmĩ <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 3:1-18">3:1-18</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mũtũũrĩre wa wĩhokeku <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 4:1-17">4:1-17</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kũmenereria ũtonga <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 5:1-6">5:1-6</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Kũrĩkĩrĩria kwa wĩhokeku <char style="ior"><ref loc="JAS 5:7-20">5:7-20</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 15:13">Atũm 15:13</ref>; <ref loc="TIT 1:1">Tit 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 32:26">Gũcook 32:26</ref> </char>
    </note>Nĩ niĩ Jakubu, ndungata ya Ngai na ya Mwathani Jesũ Kristũ,</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Ndĩramwandĩkĩra inyuĩ a mĩhĩrĩga ĩrĩa ikũmi na ĩĩrĩ mũhurunjĩtwo thĩ yothe:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Nĩndamũgeithia.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mathĩĩna na Magerio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:12">Math 5:12</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, rĩrĩa rĩothe mwakorwo nĩ magerio ma mĩthemba mĩingĩ-rĩ, tuagai atĩ ũguo nĩ gĩkeno gĩtheri. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1PE 1:7">1Pet 1:7</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:36">Ahib 10:36</ref> </char></note>tondũ nĩmũũĩ atĩ kũgerio kwa wĩtĩkio wanyu kũrehaga gũkirĩrĩria. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Rekei gũkirĩrĩria kwanyu kũrute wĩra wakuo, nĩgeetha mũtuĩke andũ aagĩrĩru kũna na agima, mũtarĩ na ũndũ mwagĩte. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 3:9">1Ath 3:9</ref>, <ref loc="1KI 3:10">10</ref>; <ref loc="PRO 2:3-6">Thim 2:3-6</ref> </char></note>Na rĩrĩ, mũndũ wanyu angĩkorwo aagĩte ũũgĩ-rĩ, nĩahooe Ngai, ũrĩa ũheaga andũ othe na ũtaana, na atarĩ na ũũru ngoro, nake nĩekũheo ũũgĩ ũcio. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 11:24">Mar 11:24</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩa ekũhooya-rĩ, nĩahooe etĩkĩtie, na ndagathanganie, tondũ mũndũ ũrĩa ũthanganagia ahaana ta ikũmbĩ rĩa iria inene, rĩrĩa rĩhurutagwo nĩ rũhuho na rĩkarũgarũũgio. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Mũndũ ũcio ndageciirie atĩ nĩakaheo kĩndũ o nakĩ nĩ Mwathani; <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 119:113">Thab 119:113</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 2:14">2Pet 2:14</ref> </char></note>ũcio nĩ mũndũ wa ngoro igĩrĩ, ũtarĩ hĩndĩ akindagĩria maũndũ-inĩ mothe marĩa ekaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ ũrĩa wĩnyiihagia aagĩrĩirwo nĩ kwĩraha nĩ ũndũ nĩatũũgĩrĩtio. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 7:31">1Akor 7:31</ref></char></note>No ũrĩa mũtongu nĩerahage nĩ ũndũ wa kũnyiihio gwake, tondũ agaathira ta ihũa rĩa gĩthaka. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo riũa rĩrathaga rĩrĩ na ũrugarĩ mũhiũ wa gũcina narĩo rĩkahoohia mũmera; nakĩo kĩro kĩaguo gĩgaitĩka na ũthaka waguo ũkanangwo. Ũguo no taguo mũndũ ũrĩa mũtongu akaahwererekera o akĩrutaga wĩra wake.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 22:1">Kĩam 22:1</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 9:25">1Akor 9:25</ref> </char>
    </note>Kũrathimwo-rĩ, nĩ mũndũ ũrĩa ũũmagĩrĩria rĩrĩa ekũgerio, tondũ aatooria magerio, nĩakaheo thũmbĩ ya muoyo ĩrĩa Ngai erĩire arĩa mamwendete.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwagerio, mũndũ o naũ ndakanoige atĩrĩ, “Ngai nĩarangeria.” Nĩgũkorwo Ngai ndangĩhota kũgerio nĩ ũũru, o nake mwene ndageragia mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ; <verse number="14" style="v"/>no rĩrĩ, mũndũ nĩkũgerio ageragio hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ekũguucĩrĩrio na akaheenererio nĩ merirĩria make mooru. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 15:35">Ayub 15:35</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 7:14">Thab 7:14</ref></char></note>Namo merirĩria marĩkia kũgĩa nda, maciaraga mehia; namo mehia hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maakũra biũ, magaciara gĩkuũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ inyuĩ nyenda mũno-rĩ, mũtikanaheenio. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 85:12">Thab 85:12</ref>; <ref loc="GEN 1:16">Kĩam 1:16</ref></char></note>Kĩheo gĩothe kĩega na gĩkinyanĩru kiumaga igũrũ, gĩikũrũkĩte kuuma kũrĩ Ithe wa motheri ma igũrũ, ũrĩa ũtagarũrũkaga ta ciĩruru iria igarũrũkaga. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 1:13">Joh 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="REV 14:4">Kũg 14:4</ref> </char></note>Nĩwe watũciarire nĩ kwenda na ũndũ wa ũhoro-ũrĩa-wa-ma, nĩguo tũtuĩke ta maciaro ma mbere ma indo ciothe iria ombire.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũthikĩrĩria na Gwĩka</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 10:19">Thim 10:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ inyuĩ nyenda mũno, menyai ũũ: O mũndũ nĩahiũhage gũthikĩrĩria, no ndakahiũhage kwaria o na kana kũrakara, <verse number="20" style="v"/>nĩgũkorwo marakara ma mũndũ matirehaga mũtũũrĩre wa ũthingu ũrĩa Ngai endaga. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio-rĩ, eheriai maũndũ mothe marĩ magigi, na ũũru ũrĩa ũkĩrĩrĩirie kũingĩha, na mwĩnyiihĩtie, mwĩtĩkĩre kiugo kĩrĩa kĩhaandĩtwo thĩinĩ wanyu, o kĩrĩa kĩngĩmũhonokia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>Mũtigatuĩke o a gũthikagĩrĩria kiugo tu, no tuĩkai a gwĩka ũrĩa kiugĩte, nĩguo mũtikeheenie inyuĩ ene. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe ũthikagĩrĩria kiugo no ndekaga ũrĩa kiugĩte-rĩ, ahaana ta mũndũ ũrĩa wĩroraga ũthiũ na gĩcicio, <verse number="24" style="v"/>na thuutha wa kwĩrora, agethiĩra na akariganĩrwo o narua nĩ ũrĩa ahaana. <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 2:12">Jak 2:12</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 13:17">Joh 13:17</ref> </char></note>No mũndũ ũrĩa ũroraga wega watho ũrĩa mũkinyanĩru kũna ũrĩa ũheanaga wĩyathi, na agathiĩ na mbere gwĩka ũguo, atekũriganĩrwo nĩ ũrĩa aiguĩte no akawĩkaga-rĩ, ũcio nĩarĩrathimagĩrwo maũndũ marĩa ekaga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v"/>Mũndũ o wothe angĩĩtua mũndũ wa ndini no aremwo nĩ gwatha rũrĩmĩ rwake-rĩ, mũndũ ũcio nĩ kwĩheenia eheenagia, na ũndini wake nĩ wa tũhũ. <verse number="27" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 25:36">Math 25:36</ref></char></note>Ũndini ũrĩa Ngai Ithe witũ etĩkagĩra atĩ nĩ mũtheru na ndũrĩ na mahĩtia nĩ ũyũ: nĩ kũroraga ciana cia ngoriai na atumia a ndigwa hĩndĩ ĩrĩa marĩ mathĩĩna-inĩ mao, na ningĩ mũndũ etheemage ndagathũkio nĩ maũndũ ma gũkũ thĩ.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kũgirio Gũthuurania Andũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 2:8">1Akor 2:8</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ta etĩkia thĩinĩ wa Mwathani witũ Jesũ Kristũ, o we ũrĩa ũrĩ riiri-rĩ, tigagai gũthutũkanagia andũ nĩ ũndũ wa maũthĩ mao. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Tondũ-rĩ, ĩ hihi kũngĩũka mũndũ kĩũngano-inĩ kĩanyu ekĩrĩte gĩcũhĩ gĩa thahabu na nguo njega, na gũũke mũndũ mũthĩĩni ũtehumbĩte nguo njega-rĩ, <verse number="3" style="v"/>na inyuĩ mũhe ũcio wĩhumbĩte nguo njega gĩtĩĩo, mũmwĩre atĩrĩ, “Haha harĩ na gĩtĩ kĩega gĩa gũikarĩra,” no mwĩre mũndũ ũcio mũthĩĩni atĩrĩ, “Wee rũgama harĩa,” kana, “Ikara haha magũrũ-inĩ makwa,” <verse number="4" style="v"/>githĩ mũtiagĩthutũkania inyuĩ ene, na mwatuĩka atuanĩri ciira marĩ na meciiria mooru?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JOB 34:19">Ayub 34:19</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 12:21">Luk 12:21</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ inyuĩ nyenda mũno, ta thikĩrĩriai: Githĩ Ngai ndathuurĩte arĩa monagwo marĩ athĩĩni gũkũ thĩ nĩguo matuĩke itonga ũhoro-inĩ wa wĩtĩkio na magaĩrwo ũthamaki ũrĩa erĩire arĩa mamwendete? <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 11:22">1Akor 11:22</ref> </char></note>No inyuĩ nĩ mũnyararaga arĩa athĩĩni. Githĩ ti itonga imũhinyagĩrĩria? Githĩ ti o mamũtwaraga igooti-inĩ na hinya? <verse number="7" style="v"/>Ningĩ githĩ ti o macambagia rĩĩtwa rĩrĩa rĩrĩ gĩtĩĩo, o rĩu rĩa ũrĩa mũrĩ ake?</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LEV 19:18">Alaw 19:18</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 5:43">Math 5:43</ref> </char>
    </note>Angĩkorwo nĩmũhingagia watho ũrĩa mũtue nĩ mũthamaki ũrĩa wandĩkĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ atĩrĩ, “Enda mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ o ta ũrĩa wĩyendete wee mwene,” nĩmwĩkaga wega. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 1:17">Gũcook 1:17</ref> </char></note>No angĩkorwo mũtĩĩagĩra andũ maũthĩ-rĩ, nĩ kwĩhia mwĩhagia na mũrĩ atuĩre nĩ watho atĩ mũrĩ aagarari watho. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:19">Math 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 3:10">Agal 3:10</ref> </char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ũrĩa wothe ũhingagia watho wothe, no akahĩngwo nĩ kaũndũ o kamwe ka guo, mũndũ ũcio nĩagararĩte watho wothe. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 20:14">Thaam 20:14</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 20:13">20:13</ref> </char></note>Tondũ ũrĩa woigire atĩ, “Ndũkanatharanie,” nowe woigire atĩ, “Ndũkanoragane.” Rĩu-rĩ, ũngĩaga gũtharania no ũragane-rĩ, wee nĩũtuĩkĩte mwagarari wa watho.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 16:27">Math 16:27</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:25">Jak 1:25</ref> </char>
    </note>Aragiai na mwĩkage maũndũ manyu o ta mũrĩ arĩa magaatuĩrwo ciira nĩ watho ũrĩa ũheanaga wĩyathi, <verse number="13" style="v"/>tondũ mũndũ ũrĩa ũtuanĩire ciira atekũiguanĩra tha-rĩ, ũcio nake agaatuĩrwo ciira atekũiguĩrwo tha. Nacio tha nĩitooragia ũtuanĩri wa ciira!</para>
  <para style="s1">Wĩtĩkio na Ciĩko</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 7:26">Math 7:26</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, gũkĩrĩ na uumithio ũrĩkũ mũndũ angiuga atĩ arĩ na wĩtĩkio, no ndarĩ na ciĩko? Wĩtĩkio ũcio wakĩmũhonokia? <verse number="15" style="v"/>Mũrũ wa Ithe witũ kana mwarĩ wa Ithe witũ angĩkorwo ndarĩ na nguo cia kwĩhumba, kana irio cia kũrĩa o mũthenya, <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 3:17">1Joh 3:17</ref>, <ref loc="1JN 3:18">18</ref> </char></note>nake ũmwe wanyu amwĩre atĩrĩ, “Thiĩ na wega; gĩa na ũrugarĩ na ũrĩe wega,” no ndarĩ ũndũ aamũteithia naguo mabataro-inĩ make ma mwĩrĩ-rĩ, ũndũ ũcio ũkĩrĩ na uumithio ũrĩkũ? <verse number="17" style="v"/>Ũguo no taguo wĩtĩkio mũtheri ũtarĩ na ciĩko ũhaana, nĩ mũkuũ guo mwene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:28">Arom 3:28</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 3:13">Jak 3:13</ref> </char>
    </note>No mũndũ no oige atĩrĩ, “Wee-rĩ, ũrĩ na wĩtĩkio; na niĩ ndĩ na ciĩko.”</para>
  <para style="p">Nyonia wĩtĩkio waku ũrĩa ũtarĩ na ciĩko, na niĩ nĩngũkuonia wĩtĩkio wakwa na ũndũ wa ũrĩa njĩkaga. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="DEU 6:4">Gũcook 6:4</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 8:29">Math 8:29</ref> </char></note>Wee nĩwĩtĩkĩtie atĩ Ngai no ũmwe. Ũguo nĩ wega! O nacio ndaimono nĩciĩtĩkĩtie ũguo, na ikainaina.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>Wee kĩrimũ gĩkĩ, nĩ ũira ũrakĩenda wa kuonania atĩ wĩtĩkio ũtarĩ na ciĩko nĩ wa tũhũ? <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 11:9">Kĩam 11:9</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 11:12">12</ref> </char></note>Githĩ Iburahĩmu, ithe witũ wa tene, ndaatuirwo mũthingu nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa eekire rĩrĩa aarutire mũriũ Isaaka kĩgongona-inĩ? <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 11:17">Ahib 11:17</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 1:3">1Athe 1:3</ref> </char></note>Mũtigũkĩona atĩ wĩtĩkio wake nĩ warutire wĩra hamwe na ciĩko ciake, naguo wĩtĩkio wake ũgĩtuuo mũiganĩru kũna nĩ ũndũ wa ciĩko icio ciake. <verse number="23" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:23 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 15:6">Kĩam 15:6</ref>; <ref loc="2CH 20:7">2Maũ 20:7</ref> </char></note>Namo Maandĩko makĩhingio marĩa moigĩte atĩrĩ, “Iburahĩmu agĩĩtĩkia Ngai, nakuo gwĩtĩkia kũu gũgĩtũma atuuo mũthingu,” nake agĩĩtwo mũrata wa Ngai. <verse number="24" style="v"/>Nĩmũkuona atĩ mũndũ atuagwo mũthingu nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa ekaga, no ti ũndũ wa wĩtĩkio wiki.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:25 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HEB 11:31">Ahib 11:31</ref> </char>
    </note>O nake Rahabu ũrĩa warĩ mũmaraya-rĩ, githĩ ndaatuirwo mũthingu nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa eekire hĩndĩ ĩrĩa aanyiitire athigaani arĩa ũgeni na akĩmoonereria njĩra ĩngĩ ya kũũrĩra? <verse number="26" style="v"/>O ta ũrĩa mwĩrĩ ũtarĩ na roho ũrĩ mũkuũ-rĩ, ũguo noguo wĩtĩkio ũtarĩ ciĩko ũrĩ mũkuũ.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Gwatha Rũrĩmĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 4:11">Aef 4:11</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 7:15">Math 7:15</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ti aingĩ anyu magĩrĩirwo nĩ gũtuĩka arutani, tondũ nĩ mũũĩ atĩ ithuĩ arĩa tũrutanaga nĩtũgaatuĩrwo ituĩro rĩa hinya gũkĩra andũ arĩa angĩ. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1KI 8:46">1Ath 8:46</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 12:37">Math 12:37</ref> </char></note>Ithuothe nĩtũhĩngĩcagwo nĩ maũndũ maingĩ. Mũndũ angĩkorwo ndarĩ na mahĩtia thĩinĩ wa maũndũ marĩa aragia-rĩ, ũcio nĩ mũkinyanĩru kũna, na nĩahotete kũriĩra mwĩrĩ wake wothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 32:9">Thab 32:9</ref> </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa twekĩra mbarathi mĩkwa tũnua nĩguo itwathĩkĩre-rĩ, nĩtũhotaga kũgarũra nyamũ ĩyo ĩrĩ yothe. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Ningĩ ta rorai ũhoro wa marikabu ũrĩ ta kĩonereria. O na gũtuĩka nĩ nene na itwaragwo nĩ rũhuho rũrĩ na hinya-rĩ, nĩigarũragwo na gathukani kanini, ikarorio o kũrĩa mũtwarithia wacio ekwenda gũciroria. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 12:3-4">Thab 12:3-4</ref> </char></note>Ũguo no taguo rũrĩmĩ rũhaana. Nĩ kĩĩga kĩnini kĩa mwĩrĩ, no nĩ rwĩĩkagĩrĩra mũno. Ta mwĩciiriei ũrĩa mũtitũ mũnene ũgwatagio mwaki nĩ gathandĩ o kanini. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 16:27">Thim 16:27</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 15:11">Math 15:11</ref> </char></note>Ningĩ rũrĩmĩ nĩ mwaki, tondũ rũiyũrĩte mĩthemba yothe ya maũndũ ma waganu thĩinĩ wa ciĩga cia mwĩrĩ. Rũthũkagia mwĩrĩ wothe, rũkagwatia mwaki mũtũũrĩre wothe wa mũndũ, naruo rwene rũkoragwo rũmundĩtio mwaki nĩ Jehanamu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>Nyamũ cia mĩthemba yothe, na nyoni, na nyamũ iria itambaga thĩ, na nyamũ cia iria-inĩ rĩrĩa inene ciothe nĩihooreragio na cianahoorerio nĩ mũndũ, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 140:3">Thab 140:3</ref> </char></note>no gũtirĩ mũndũ o na ũrĩkũ ũngĩhota kũhooreria rũrĩmĩ. Nĩruo kĩndũ kĩũru gĩtangĩkindĩria na rũiyũrĩtwo nĩ thumu wa kũũragana.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GEN 1:26">Kĩam 1:26</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 1:27">27</ref> </char>
    </note>Tũgoocaga Mwathani, o we Ithe witũ, na rũrĩmĩ, na tũkaruma andũ naruo, o acio mombĩtwo marĩ na mũhianĩre wa Ngai. <verse number="10" style="v"/>Kanua o kau-rĩ, no ko koimaga ũgooci na gakoima irumi. Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, ũguo tiguo kwagĩrĩire gũtuĩka. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Kaĩ maaĩ mega na maaĩ ma cumbĩ mangĩtherũka kuuma gĩthima kĩmwe? <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mũkũyũ no ũhote gũciara ndamaiyũ, kana mũthabibũ ũciare ngũyũ? O nakĩo gĩthima kĩa maaĩ ma cumbĩ gĩtingĩtherũka maaĩ mega.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mĩthemba Ĩĩrĩ ya Ũũgĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JAS 2:18">Jak 2:18</ref> </char>
    </note>Thĩinĩ wanyu-rĩ, nũũ ũrĩ na ũũgĩ na agataũkĩrwo nĩ maũndũ? Mũndũ ũcio nĩakĩonanie maũndũ macio na ũndũ wa mũtũũrĩre wake mwega, na ciĩko ciĩkĩĩtwo na njĩra ya kwĩnyiihia kũrĩa kuumanaga na ũũgĩ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>No mũngĩkorwo ngoro-inĩ cianyu nĩ mũtũũragia ũiru na ũhoro wa kwenda kwĩyambatĩria-rĩ, mũtikae kwĩrahĩra ũndũ ũcio kana mũtuĩke a gũkaana ũhoro wa ma. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 3:17">Jak 3:17</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 4:1">1Tim 4:1</ref> </char></note>“Ũũgĩ” ta ũcio tiguo ũikũrũkaga uumĩte igũrũ, no nĩ wa thĩ ĩno, na ti wa kĩĩroho, ũcio nĩ ũũgĩ wa mũcukani. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩgũkorwo harĩa harĩ na ũiru na ũhoro wa kwenda kwĩyambatĩria-rĩ, hau nĩho hakoragwo na ngũĩ na ciĩko ciothe cia waganu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>No ũũgĩ ũrĩa uumaga igũrũ o mbere nĩ mũtheru; ningĩ nĩwendete thayũ, na nĩũcaayanagĩra, na nĩwĩnyiihagia, na nĩ ũiyũrĩtwo nĩ tha na maciaro mega, ningĩ ndũthutũkanagia, na ndũrĩ ũhinga. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 11:18">Thim 11:18</ref> </char></note>Nao ateithũrani arĩa mahaandaga thayũ-rĩ, magethaga maciaro ma ũthingu.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Mwĩnyiihagĩriei Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 7:23">Arom 7:23</ref> </char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, nĩ kĩĩ gĩtũmaga kũgĩe na mbaara na ngũĩ thĩinĩ wanyu? Githĩ itiumaga merirĩria-inĩ manyu marĩa marũaga thĩinĩ wanyu? <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 5:21-22">Math 5:21-22</ref> </char></note>Mwĩriragĩria kĩndũ no mũkaaga kũgĩa nakĩo. Ningĩ mũũraganaga na mũgacumĩkĩra, no mũtingĩhota kũgĩa na kĩrĩa mũkwenda. Mũtetanagia na mũkarũa. Mũgakĩaga kuona kĩndũ tondũ wa kwaga kũhooya Ngai. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa mwahooya-rĩ, nĩmwagaga kũheo, tondũ mũhooyaga mũrĩ na muoroto mũũru, tondũ mwendaga mũitangage kĩrĩa mwaheo na maũndũ ma gwĩkenia.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 54:5">Isa 54:5</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 2:15">Joh 2:15</ref> </char>
    </note>Inyuĩ atharania aya, kaĩ mũtooĩ atĩ kũgĩa ũrata na thĩ nĩ kũgĩa ũthũ na Ngai? Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mũndũ o wothe ũthuuraga kũgĩa ũrata na thĩ nĩkũgĩa ũthũ ya Ngai. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Kana mũgwĩciiria Maandĩko maaragia ũhoro ũtarĩ na gĩtũmi, atĩ roho ũrĩa Ngai aatũmire ũtũũrage thĩinĩ witũ nĩ ũiguaga ũiru mũno? <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 3:34">Thim 3:34</ref> </char></note>No nĩatũheaga wega wake makĩria. Kĩu nĩkĩo gĩtũmaga Maandĩko moige atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Ngai nĩareganaga na arĩa etĩĩi</para>
  <para style="q2">no arĩa menyiihagia nĩo aheaga wega wake.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 5:6-9">1Pet 5:6-9</ref> </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio mwĩnyiihagĩriei Ngai. Reganagai na mũcukani, nake nĩekũmũũrĩra. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 1:16">Isa 1:16</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:8">Jak 1:8</ref> </char></note>Kuhĩrĩriai Ngai, nake nĩekũmũkuhĩrĩria. Mwĩthambei moko manyu inyuĩ ehia, na mũtherie ngoro cianyu inyuĩ andũ a ngoro igĩrĩ.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">4:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Athĩnjĩri-Ngai matanakuhĩrĩria Ngai Hema-inĩ-ya-Gũtũnganwo nĩmambaga gwĩthamba magũrũ na moko mbakũri-inĩ ya gĩcango arĩ njĩra ya gwĩtheria kĩĩroho (Thaam 30:17-21).</char></note> <verse number="9" style="v"/>Iguai kĩeha, mũcakae, na mũgirĩke. Garũrai mĩtheko yanyu ĩtuĩke macakaya, nakĩo gĩkeno kĩanyu kĩgarũrũke gĩtuĩke kĩeha. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JAS 4:6">Jak 4:6</ref> </char></note>Mwĩnyiihĩriei Mwathani, nake nĩekũmũtũũgĩria.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 2:1">1Pet 2:1</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, tigai gũcambania mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ. Ũrĩa wothe waragia ũhoro wa gũcambia mũrũ kana mwarĩ wa ithe kana akamũtuĩra ciira-rĩ, nĩ watho acambagia na akaũtuĩra ciira. Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ũgũtuĩra watho ciira-rĩ, ndũkoragwo ũkĩhingia watho, no ũkoragwo ũrĩ mũtuanĩri ciira. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 3:22">Isa 3:22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 10:28">Math 10:28</ref> </char></note>Kũrĩ Mũheani wa watho, na Mũtuanĩri ciira o ũmwe, o we ũrĩa ũrĩ na ũhoti wa kũhonokia na kũniinana. No wee-rĩ, ũkĩrĩ ũ nĩguo ũtuĩre mũndũ ũrĩa ũngĩ ciira?</para>
  <para style="s1">Kwĩraha nĩ ũndũ wa Rũciũ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PRO 27:1">Thim 27:1</ref> </char>
    </note>Rĩu ta thikĩrĩriai, inyuĩ mugaga atĩrĩ: “Ũmũthĩ kana rũciũ nĩtũgũthiĩ itũũra rĩna tũikare kuo mwaka ũmwe, tũrute wĩra wa wonjoria kuo, tũgĩe na mbeeca.” <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 7:7">Ayub 7:7</ref> </char></note>No rĩrĩ, inyuĩ mũtiũĩ ũrĩa gũgaatuĩka rũciũ. Muoyo wanyu ũkĩrĩ kĩ? Inyuĩ mũrĩ o kĩbii kĩrĩa kĩonekaga o kahinda kanini, gĩgacooka gĩgathira biũ. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 18:21">Atũm 18:21</ref> </char></note>Handũ ha ũguo-rĩ, mwagĩrĩirwo nĩ kugaga atĩrĩ, “Mwathani angĩenda-rĩ, nĩ tũgũtũũra muoyo na twĩkage ũndũ ũyũ na ũyũ.” <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 5:6">1Akor 5:6</ref> </char></note>No rĩu inyuĩ nĩ kwĩraha mwĩrahaga mũrĩ na nguthi. Mwĩraho ta ũcio wothe nĩ mũũru. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 12:47">Luk 12:47</ref> </char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo, mũndũ wothe ũũĩ gwĩka wega na ndekaga-rĩ, ũcio nĩ kwĩhia ehagia.</para>
  <chapter number="5" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Itonga Gũkaanio Kũhinyanĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 6:24">Luk 6:24</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Rĩu ta thikĩrĩriai, inyuĩ itonga ici, rĩrai na mũgirĩke tondũ wa mathĩĩna marĩa maramũkora. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 13:28">Ayub 13:28</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 6:19">Math 6:19</ref>, <ref loc="MAT 6:20">20</ref> </char></note>Ũtonga wanyu nĩ ũbuthĩte, nacio nguo cianyu nĩ ndĩe nĩ memenyi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">5:2 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Matukũ-inĩ ma tene nguo ciataragwo taarĩ njĩra ĩmwe ya ũtonga (Atũm 20:33).</char></note> <verse number="3" style="v"/>Thahabu na betha cianyu nĩ irootete. Kũroota gwacio nĩ ũira wa atĩ nĩireganĩte na inyuĩ, na nĩikũrĩa mĩĩrĩ yanyu imũniine o ta mwaki. Inyuĩ mwĩigĩire mũthithũ mũingĩ wa matukũ ma kũrigĩrĩria. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LEV 19:13">Alaw 19:13</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 24:15">Gũcook 24:15</ref> </char></note>Atĩrĩrĩ! Mĩcaara ĩrĩa mwaregire kũrĩha aruti a wĩra arĩa maamũrĩmĩire mĩgũnda nĩĩramũkaĩra. Gũkaya kwa arĩa maamũgetheire irio nĩgũkinyĩire matũ ma Mwathani Mwene hinya wothe. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EZK 16:49">Ezek 16:49</ref>; <ref loc="JER 12:3">Jer 12:3</ref> </char></note>Mũtũũrĩte gũkũ thĩ na mĩago na mũgĩĩkenagia. Inyuĩ mwĩnoretie nĩ ũndũ wa mũthenya wa gũthĩnjwo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Inyuĩ nĩ mũtuĩrĩire andũ ciira na mũkamooraga matarĩ na mahĩtia, o acio matarĩ ũũru na inyuĩ.</para>
  <para style="s1">Gũkirĩrĩria Mathĩĩna-inĩ</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:7 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 1:7">1Akor 1:7</ref>; <ref loc="GAL 6:9">Agal 6:9</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 11:14">Gũcook 11:14</ref> </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, kiragĩrĩriai, o nginya rĩrĩa Mwathani agooka. Ta rorai ũrĩa mũrĩmi etagĩrĩra mũgũnda wake ũrute irio iria irĩ bata, na agakirĩrĩria nginya ciurĩrwo nĩ mbura ya mbere o na ya keerĩ ategũthethũka. <verse number="8" style="v"/>O na inyuĩ-rĩ, kirĩrĩriai na mwĩhaande wega, tondũ Mwathani arĩ hakuhĩ gũũka. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 24:33">Math 24:33</ref> </char></note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, tigagai gũtetania, nĩgeetha mũtikanatuĩrwo ciira. Mũtuanĩri ciira arũngiĩ o mũrango-inĩ!</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:12">Math 5:12</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mwĩrutei na maũndũ marĩa mooru anabii meekirwo, o acio maaragia thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani, naguo ũhoro ũcio ũtuĩke kĩonereria kĩanyu gĩa gũkirĩrĩria rĩrĩa mũkũnyamario. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JOB 42:10">Ayub 42:10</ref>, <ref loc="JOB 42:12-17">12-17</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 34:6">Thaam 34:6</ref> </char></note>O ta ũrĩa mũũĩ, acio maakirĩrĩirie-rĩ, tũmatuaga arathime. Nĩmũiguĩte ũhoro wa gũkirĩrĩria kwa Ayubu, na nĩmuonete ũrĩa Mwathani eekire marigĩrĩrio-inĩ. Mwathani aiyũrĩtwo nĩ ũtugi na tha.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 5:34-37">Math 5:34-37</ref> </char>
    </note>Ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, igũrũ rĩa maũndũ mothe-rĩ, tigagai kwĩhĩta. Mũtikanehĩte na igũrũ kana na thĩ, o na kana na kĩndũ kĩngĩ o na kĩ. Inyuĩ-rĩ, mwoiga “Ĩĩ” nĩĩtuĩke ĩĩ, na mwoiga “Aca” nĩĩtuĩke aca, nĩguo mũtikae gũtuĩrwo ciira.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ihooya rĩa Wĩtĩkio</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>Nĩ harĩ mũndũ thĩinĩ wanyu wonete ũũru? Ũcio nĩahooe. Nĩ harĩ mũndũ ũkenete? Ũcio nĩaine nyĩmbo cia kũgooca. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 6:13">Mar 6:13</ref> </char></note>Nĩ harĩ mũndũ thĩinĩ wanyu mũrũaru? Ũcio nĩete athuuri a kanitha mamũhooere na mamũhake maguta thĩinĩ wa rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Namo mahooya mangĩhooywo na wĩtĩkio nĩ megũtũma mũndũ ũcio mũrũaru ahone; Mwathani nĩekũmwarahũra. Angĩkorwo ehĩtie-rĩ, nĩekũrekerwo mehia make. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio umbũranagĩrai mehia manyu o mũndũ na ũrĩa ũngĩ, na mũhooyanagĩre nĩgeetha mũhonagio. Ihooya rĩa mũndũ mũthingu nĩ rĩrĩ hinya na nĩ rĩtũmaga maũndũ manene mekĩke.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:17 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 14:15">Atũm 14:15</ref>; <ref loc="1KI 17:1">1Ath 17:1</ref> </char>
    </note>Elija aarĩ mũndũ o ta ithuĩ. Nake nĩahooire Ngai na kĩyo atĩ mbura ndĩkoire, nayo mbura ndĩoirire bũrũri-inĩ ũcio ihinda rĩa mĩaka ĩtatũ na nuthu. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Ningĩ agĩcooka akĩhooya, nakuo matu-inĩ gũkiuma mbura, nayo thĩ ĩgĩciara maciaro mayo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">5:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 18:15">Math 18:15</ref> </char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ, mũndũ ũmwe wanyu angĩagaga oime ũhoro-inĩ wa ma nake mũndũ ũngĩ amũgarũre-rĩ, <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">5:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:14">Arom 11:14</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 4:8">1Pet 4:8</ref> </char></note>ririkanai ũũ: Mũndũ ũrĩa wothe ũgarũraga mwĩhia kuuma njĩra-inĩ yake njũru-rĩ, nĩkũmũhonokia akaamũhonokia kuuma harĩ gĩkuũ na ahumbĩre mehia maingĩ.</para>
</usx>
